nTupleTD

Class TDParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • nTupleTD.TDParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class TDParams
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    This class contains all params needed for a TD-Agent with a N-Tuple Value function. The Interface Serializable is implemented, so that these params can be saved to HDD.
    Author:
    Markus Thill
